dct_title_s: Maui, Kauai & Molokai : scale 1:100,000 / International Travel Maps; edited by Yusuke Ujimiya, Mark Ramsay, Tran Dinh Cuong, Ding Nguyen, Doc Trinh, Phuong Vu, Tran Hung Nam; Lan Joyce, editor in chief. (Kauai, Molokai, Ni'ihau)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by gradient and bathymetric tints, contours, and spot heights. Includes index, legend, text, and location map. Map is waterproof. Insets : Kapalua --- Kaunakakai --- Kihei-Wailea --- Lahaina --- Lanai --- Lanai City --- Lihue --- Po'ipu, Koloa --- Wailuku, Kahului.
